==== ENTRY 4 ====
HEADWORD: Mad
<hw>Mad</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To be mad; to go mad; to rave. See
<er>Madding</er>.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Festus said with great voice, Paul thou <qex>maddest</qex>.</q>
